title: FBI Confirms Zodiac Killer Cypher Has Been Cracked
author: The Infographics Show
description:
2020 has had no shortage of surprises and just before the year wraps up another bombshell has been dropped as the FBI confirms the Zodiac Killer's cypher has finally been cracked! You can't miss this shocking reveal of what the Zodiac's secret message finally says! Will this insane discovery finally lead to the real identity of the mystery killer? You have to watch today's epic new video to find out!

Check out the Youtube video's of people who solved it: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-1oQLPRE21o&feature=youtu.be and subscribe to their channel!!! Amazing work!
